example.eg: Many actresses and actors are well known all around the world.
example.egtrans: 许多女演员和男演员是世界闻名的。

example.eg: It's a well-known fact that sea water is salty.
example.egtrans: 人所共知的事实是海水是咸的。

trans_examp.trans_cn: 人所共知的, 为大家所知道且认可的

dsense.name: well-known fact
dsense.guideword: ([sth] of which many people are aware)

example.eg: It is a well-known fact that smoking causes cancer.
